title: Supreme Court Allows Texas To Move Forward With Trump-Backed Gerrymander
description: The Texas congressional map enacted last summer at Trump’s urging was engineered to give Republicans five additional House seats.
content: WASHINGTON (AP) The Supreme Court on Thursday came to the rescue of Texas Republicans, allowing next years elections to be held under the states congressional redistricting plan favorable to the GOP … [+3354 chars]
